## ğŸ§ª Testing

Run the comprehensive test suite:

```bash
python -m vargula
```

Or create your own tests:

```python
import vargula as ts

# Disable for testing
ts.disable()
assert ts.style("Test", color="red") == "Test"

# Re-enable
ts.enable()
assert "\033[" in ts.style("Test", color="red")
```

